WEBVTT

00:00:07.194 --> 00:00:10.239 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Welcome to your Bible study!

00:00:11.490 --> 00:00:13.826 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Millions around the world enjoy

00:00:13.826 --> 00:00:16.620 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
this interactive Bible course,

00:00:16.620 --> 00:00:18.831 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and we hope you will too.

00:00:20.666 --> 00:00:23.085 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What will you learn?

00:00:24.211 --> 00:00:26.881 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How to have a happy family life,

00:00:31.427 --> 00:00:34.680 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
how to cope with anxiety,

00:00:40.269 --> 00:00:42.563 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
how to draw closer to God,

00:00:47.359 --> 00:00:50.487 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and why you can hope for a better future.

00:00:54.825 --> 00:00:57.494 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What can you expect during a study session?

00:00:59.163 --> 00:01:02.207 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Your teacher may begin the study
with a brief prayer.

00:01:03.208 --> 00:01:05.628 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Next, you will discuss

00:01:05.628 --> 00:01:08.839 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the first page of the lesson,

00:01:08.839 --> 00:01:11.133 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
read a paragraph,

00:01:11.133 --> 00:01:14.553 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and then discuss the question
for that paragraph

00:01:14.553 --> 00:01:16.764 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
before reading the next.

00:01:19.266 --> 00:01:22.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Most paragraphs
have key Bible verses highlighted.

00:01:24.229 --> 00:01:28.275 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Your teacher will also read
and discuss with you other verses,

00:01:28.275 --> 00:01:31.278 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
especially those marked “Read.”

00:01:32.905 --> 00:01:36.951 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Next, read and discuss
the section “Dig Deeper.”

00:01:38.702 --> 00:01:40.704 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
By reading scriptures,

00:01:40.704 --> 00:01:42.790 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
discussing questions,

00:01:42.790 --> 00:01:46.835 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and watching videos
that are available to you,

00:01:46.835 --> 00:01:50.381 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you will learn more
about how the topic of the lesson

00:01:50.381 --> 00:01:52.800 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
can help you personally.

00:01:55.094 --> 00:01:57.763 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Finally, after reviewing the lesson,

00:01:57.763 --> 00:02:02.434 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
your teacher may say a prayer
to end the study session.

00:02:04.478 --> 00:02:07.731 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How often do you need
to have a study session?

00:02:07.731 --> 00:02:10.567 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And how long should each session last?

00:02:11.944 --> 00:02:14.238 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is flexible.

00:02:14.238 --> 00:02:17.825 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But to maximize the benefits of this course,

00:02:17.825 --> 00:02:21.495 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we recommend covering
at least one lesson per week.

00:02:25.874 --> 00:02:29.878 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Bible is the world’s best guide
to a happy life.

00:02:31.380 --> 00:02:35.843 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Discover how it can help you
in this interactive Bible course.

